Subject: [PATCH 0/3 net-next] unix: report mnt_id and file system path for unix sockets

Currently we don't have a way to get a real path to a unix socket.
This set adds this ability to the socket diag interface.

In CRIU we need this functionality to dump and restore unix sockets.

Andrei Vagin (3):
  fs: add a function to get mnt_id for vfsmount
  unix: report mnt_id for unix sockets via socket_diag
  unix: report file system path for unix sockets via socket_diag

